snippet.title: Fortnite Battle Royale Chapter 6 Season 4: Shock 'N Awesome | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
You’re being tossed into the buggiest season yet with Fortnite’s Battle Royale Chapter 6, Season 4: Shock ’N Awesome!

The bugs out there? Vicious, relentless, swarming. The Island is an absolute mess of goopy nests and egg sacs. Prepare to stomp and smash the swarm with the O.X.R., the Island’s anti-bug military defense force.

If you’re serious about stomping roachies, then you’ll want to pick up new weapons issues by O.X.R. ike the Leadspitter 3000 minigun, Sweeper Shotgun, O.X.R. Rifle, Wrecker Revolver, or the laser-guided Swarmstrike rocket launcher.

And don’t forget about leveling up with the Shock ‘N Awesome Battle Pass to knock the socks off the swarm with style! New Outfits include:

UNSC Spartan
Yoo-mi
Agent Patch
Battle Gamer Mae
Lt. Ripp Slade
Onyx Winter
Green Ranger

Time to pelt pests, eliminating opposing enemies, and loot those Chests.

Good luck out there, soldier!

snippet.title: HIM | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
What would you sacrifice to become the greatest of all time?

From Oscar® winner Jordan Peele and Monkeypaw Productions, producers of the landmark horror films Get Out, Us, Candyman and Nope, comes a chilling journey into the inner sanctum of fame, idolatry and the pursuit of excellence at any cost, featuring an electrifying dramatic performance from Marlon Wayans (Air, Respect).

Former college wide-receiver Tyriq Withers (Atlanta, the upcoming I Know What You Did Last Summer) plays Cameron Cade, a rising-star quarterback who has devoted his life, and identity, to football. On the eve of professional football’s annual scouting Combine, Cam is attacked by an unhinged fan and suffers a potentially career-ending brain trauma.

Just when all seems lost, Cam receives a lifeline when his hero, Isaiah White (Marlon Wayans), a legendary eight-time Championship quarterback and cultural megastar, offers to train Cam at Isaiah’s isolated compound that he shares with his celebrity influencer wife, Elsie White (Julia Fox; Uncut Gems, No Sudden Move). But as Cam’s training accelerates, Isaiah’s charisma begins to curdle into something darker, sending his protégé down a disorienting rabbit hole that may cost him more than he ever bargained for.

The film features a dynamic supporting cast including alternative comedy legend Tim Heidecker (First Time Female Director, Us) and Australian comic Jim Jefferies (The Jim Jefferies Show), plus MMA heavyweight fighter Maurice Greene and hip hop phenoms Guapdad 4000 and Grammy nominee Tierra Whack, all three in their feature film debuts.

HIM is directed by Justin Tipping (Kicks) from an acclaimed Black List screenplay by Zack Akers & Skip Bronkie (creators of the sci-fi crime series Limetown) and by Justin Tipping. The film is produced by Ian Cooper (Nope, Us), Jordan Peele (Candyman, BlacKkKlansman), Win Rosenfeld (Candyman, Lovecraft Country) and Jamal M. Watson (Hala, Sprinter) for Monkeypaw Productions and is executive produced by David Kern and Monkeypaw’s Kate Oh.

Follow HIM on socials: 
https://www.instagram.com/himmovie/
https://www.facebook.com/himmovie/
https://twitter.com/himmovie/
https://www.himmovie.com/

Director:​​​Justin Tipping
Screenplay by:​Zack Akers & Skip Bronkie and Justin Tipping 
Producers: ​​​Ian Cooper, Jordan Peele, Win Rosenfeld, Jamal M. Watson

snippet.title: One Punch Man Season 3 - Official Trailer (English Subtitles)
snippet.description:
"One-Punch Man” returns with Season 3! Check out the latest trailer for the continuation of this series!

Saitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun. After three years of “special training,” he’s become so strong that he’s practically invincible. In fact, he’s too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association. One day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of Hero Association executive hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a “human monster” who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout."

snippet.title: NHL 26 Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
It’s time to show out and tell the world to Check My Game. Pre-order NHL 26 to play 7 Days Early now! https://x.ea.com/85081

Play like a superstar in EA SPORTS™ NHL® 26. That starts with ICE-Q 2.0, now powered by NHL EDGE data, so your favorite superstars think, move, and play like their on-ice selves. Data-informed Attributes and Tendencies make star players perform in true-to-life fashion, with their playstyles and decision-making game-aware and impactful. A fine-tuned and enhanced arsenal of 28 X-Factors spans five different categories and is driven by unique animations, tactical gameplay outcomes, and tiers of impact, turning each into a formidable on-ice weapon. Superstars now truly feel like superstars.

The all-new Goalie Crease Control System brings an upgraded awareness between the posts with new close-range and reflex saves that allow for readjustments in reaction to puck deflections, poke checks, and improved AI positioning, giving goalies increased control over the blue paint. In a redesigned Be A Pro mode, each choice you make impacts your career, as you live out the authentic hockey journey from rookie to superstar, with fresh storylines, characters, challenges, and cut scenes.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: RENTAL FAMILY | Official Trailer | Searchlight Pictures
snippet.description:
Discover the joy of unexpected connections. RENTAL FAMILY, starring Academy Award® winner Brendan Fraser. Premiering at @TIFF 2025, only in theaters November 21st. #RentalFamily

Set against modern-day Tokyo, RENTAL FAMILY follows an American actor (Brendan Fraser) who struggles to find purpose until he lands an unusual gig: working for a Japanese "rental family" agency, playing stand-in roles for strangers. As he immerses himself in his clients’ worlds, he begins to form genuine bonds that blur the lines between performance and reality. Confronting the moral complexities of his work, he rediscovers purpose, belonging, and the quiet beauty of human connection.

Directed by: HIKARI
Screenplay by: HIKARI, Stephen Blahut
Produced by: Eddie Vaisman, p.g.a, Julia Lebedev, p.g.a, HIKARI, p.g.a, Shin Yamaguchi, p.g.a

snippet.title: Eden - Official Trailer (2025) Jude Law, Ana de Armas, Vanessa Kirby
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for Eden, an upcoming movie starring Jude Law, Ana de Armas, Vanessa Kirby, Daniel Brühl, and Sydney Sweeney.

From Academy Award–winning director Ron Howard, Eden unravels the shocking true story of a group of disillusioned outsiders (Jude Law, Ana de Armas, Vanessa Kirby, Daniel Brühl, and Sydney Sweeney) who abandon modern society in search of a new beginning. Settling on a remote, uninhabited island, their utopian dream quickly unravels as they discover that the greatest threat isn’t the brutal climate or deadly wildlife, but each other. What follows is a chilling descent into chaos where tensions spiral, desperation takes hold, and a twisted power struggle leads to betrayal, violence, and the deaths of half the colony.

Eden is produced by Brian Grazer, Ron Howard, Karen Lunder, Stuart Ford, William M. Connor, and Patrick Newall. It is written by Noah Pink.

Eden, directed by Ron Howard, opens in theaters on August 22, 2025.

snippet.title: Castle Crashers: Painter Boss Paradise DLC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Unleash your creativity and brush off your beat ‘em up skills because Castle Crashers latest DLC is out now! Painter Boss Paradise brings a plethora of features to Castle Crashers including new art for all playable characters and weapons, a new world map, a new official character named Paint Junior, and the ability to create, play as, and share your very own custom characters using our official template! 

Available Now on Steam: https://s.team/a/3133920

Worried about missing the nostalgic feel of the original game’s art? Toggle the DLC functionality on or off from the main menu at any time to experience our classic adventure!

Get the official template here to start creating → https://www.castlecrashers.com/PBP/painting.png

Follow us on Steam → https://store.steampowered.com/developer/thebehemoth/
Follow us on socials → https://links.thebehemoth.com/
Sign up for our newsletter → https://beh.gg/news

ko.description:
스파이더맨 브랜드 뉴 데이 티저 예고편 2026. 스파이더맨 대 헐크, 스파이더맨 대 퍼니셔에 대한 설명. 헐크가 새비지 헐크로 변하는 이유, 스콜피온 장면, 새로운 주요 빌런, 토비 맥과이어, 앤드류 가필드 관련 언급 및 어벤져스 둠스데이 예고편 ► https://bit.ly/AwesomeSubscribe

스파이더맨: 새로운 날 영상, 새로운 스파이더맨 슈트 첫 공개. 헐크 발표. 브루스 배너가 스파이더맨을 도운 이유, 스파이더맨 vs 헐크, 스파이더맨 영화 속 헐크에 대한 이전 언급. 스탠 리, 인크레더블 헐크와 1980년대 스파이더맨 실사 크로스오버. 스콜피온 리턴즈, 툼스톤, 그리고 다른 새로운 악당들.

스파이더맨: 새로운 날 설명. 새로운 악당, 톰 홀랜드의 스파이더맨 변화, 어벤져스: 둠스데이 예고편과의 연관성. 새로운 캐릭터, 새로운 스파이더맨 슈트. 시네마콘에서 공개된 스파이더맨: 비욘드 더 스파이더-버스 예고편. 스파이더맨: 누아르 예고편, 세이디 싱크와 토비 맥과이어의 스파이더맨 연관성.

어벤져스 둠스데이 예고편. 로버트 다우니 주니어, 닥터 둠, 새로운 블랙 팬서, 엑스맨, 닥터 스트레인지, 어벤져스 시크릿 워즈 첫 공개, 배틀월드 MCU. 판타스틱 포, 프랭클린 리처즈. 이언 맥켈런, 매그니토, 패트릭 스튜어트, 프로페서 X, 케슬리 그래머, 비스트, 토르 리턴즈, 미스틱, 사이클롭스, 나이트크롤러, 오리지널 엑스맨.

데드풀과 울버린 이스터 에그. 케빈 파이기 마블 농담과 제4의 벽 붕괴. 데드풀과 울버린 크레딧 후 농담. 데드풀이 울버린을 구하는 이유, 엑스맨, 판타스틱 포, 그리고 데드풀이 MCU를 구하는 이유. 데드풀과 울버린이 배틀월드와 로키 시즌 2를 통해 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈를 어떻게 설정했는지, 그리고 갓 로키 크로스오버 이스터 에그로 마무리하는 방법

마블이 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈로 MCU를 리부트하는 이유. 어벤져스, 뉴 아이언맨, 울버린 같은 엑스맨 뮤턴트, 데드풀, 판타스틱 포, 고스트 라이더, 스파이더맨 등 다양한 캐릭터들이 등장하면서 어떤 변화가 있을까요?

더 많은 마블 예고편이 공개됩니다. 어벤져스 둠스데이 예고편, 스파이더맨의 새로운 날 영상, 판타스틱 포 & 슈퍼맨 영상도 곧 공개됩니다!

स्पाइडर-मैन के बिल्कुल नए दिन की फुटेज, नए स्पाइडर-मैन सूट की पहली झलक। हल्क की घोषणा। ब्रूस बैनर स्पाइडर-मैन की मदद क्यों करेंगे, स्पाइडर-मैन बनाम हल्क, स्पाइडर-मैन फिल्मों में हल्क के पिछले संदर्भ। 1980 के दशक में स्टैन ली का इनक्रेडिबल हल्क और स्पाइडर-मैन का लाइव एक्शन क्रॉसओवर। द स्कॉर्पियन रिटर्न्स, टॉम्बस्टोन, और अन्य नए खलनायक।

स्पाइडर-मैन के बिल्कुल नए दिन की व्याख्या। नए खलनायक, टॉम हॉलैंड, स्पाइडर-मैन में बदलाव, एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे ट्रेलर से कनेक्शन। नए किरदार, नया स्पाइडर-मैन सूट। सिनेमाकॉन से स्पाइडर-मैन बियॉन्ड द स्पाइडर-वर्स का ट्रेलर। स्पाइडर-मैन नॉयर ट्रेलर, सैडी सिंक, टोबी मैगुइरे, स्पाइडर-मैन कनेक्शन।

एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे ट्रेलर। रॉबर्ट डाउनी जूनियर, डॉक्टर डूम, नया ब्लैक पैंथर, एक्स-मेन, डॉक्टर स्ट्रेंज, एवेंजर्स सीक्रेट वॉर्स की पहली झलक, बैटलवर्ल्ड एमसीयू। फैंटास्टिक फोर, फ्रैंकलिन रिचर्ड्स। इयान मैककेलेन, मैग्नेटो, पैट्रिक स्टीवर्ट, प्रोफेसर एक्स, केसली ग्रामर, बीस्ट, थॉर रिटर्न्स, मिस्टिक, साइक्लोप्स, नाइटक्रॉलर, ओरिजिनल एक्स-मेन।

डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन ईस्टर एग्स। केविन फीगे, मार्वल जोक्स और चौथी दीवार का टूटना। डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन के क्रेडिट के बाद के सीन पर जोक्स। डेडपूल वूल्वरिन को क्यों बचाता है, एक्स-मेन, फैंटास्टिक फोर और डेडपूल एमसीयू को कैसे बचाते हैं। डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन बैटलवर्ल्ड और लोकी के साथ एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स की शुरुआत कैसे करते हैं? सीज़न 2 का अंत गॉड लोकी क्रॉसओवर ईस्टर एग्स के साथ।

मार्वल, एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स के साथ एमसीयू को क्यों रीबूट कर रहा है। एवेंजर्स, न्यू आयरन मैन, एक्स-मेन म्यूटेंट जैसे वूल्वरिन, डेडपूल, फैंटास्टिक फोर, घोस्ट राइडर, स्पाइडर-मैन और अन्य किरदारों के साथ क्या बदलने वाला है?

और भी कई मार्वल ट्रेलर आ रहे हैं: एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे ट्रेलर, स्पाइडर-मैन के नए दिन के और वीडियो जल्द ही आने वाले हैं, फैंटास्टिक फोर और सुपरमैन के वीडियो!

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 - Official Gameplay Overview - Amon
snippet.description:
► Pre-order Borderlands 4 Now: https://2kgam.es/Borderlands4

Amon is the Forgeknight of Borderlands 4, a resilient and highly customizable frontliner who can use his weaponized drones to adapt to any situation.

His Forge arsenal lets him attack or defend as needed, ready to pulverize enemies with a Forgehammer, slice them in twain with Forgeaxes, soak up damage with a Forgeshield, and much, much more.

Read up on Amon's Skill Tree and Action Skills in full here: https://borderlands.2k.com/borderlands-4/game-info/vault-hunters/amon/

We’ll be rolling out a Gameplay Overview, Character Short, and Vault Hunter page for all 4 Vault Hunters before launch – so stay tuned!

Borderlands 4 is now available for pre-order on PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, and Nintendo Switch 2, and pre-purchase on PC via Steam and the Epic Games Store! 💥

--------------------------------------------

Borderlands 4 is a mayhem-fueled looter shooter, jam-packed with billions of weapons, outrageous enemies, and intense co-op action. Explore a dangerous hidden planet Kairos as one of four new badass Vault Hunters.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

--------------------------------------------
FOLLOW BORDERLANDS

► Pre-order Borderlands 4 Now: https://2kgam.es/Borderlands4

Amon is the Forgeknight of Borderlands 4, a resilient and highly customizable frontliner who can use his weaponized drones to adapt to any situation.

His Forge arsenal lets him attack or defend as needed, ready to pulverize enemies with a Forgehammer, slice them in twain with Forgeaxes, soak up damage with a Forgeshield, and much, much more.

Read up on Amon's Skill Tree and Action Skills in full here: https://borderlands.2k.com/borderlands-4/game-info/vault-hunters/amon/

--------------------------------------------

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

--

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox

snippet.title: I Won't Stop Until I Get a Hand-Pay!
snippet.description:
We are BACK at the Casino with another Vlog, and we're firing on any and all games.  Our ONLY goal for this vlog is to hit a Hand-Pay, and we'll consider the Vlog a success.  Thank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you’re roasting me—I still love you. You’re all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I’ll see you in the next one! Let’s go to war.

Brettski stormed through the glimmering doors of Hollywood Casino Bangor like a man possessed. His eyes were locked on the jungle of slot machines — spinning lights, clinking coins, hollow hopes. He wasn’t here to play. He was here to win. A hand-pay — the elusive jackpot where the machine freezes, sirens blare, and a floor attendant shows up with a stack of money like it’s sacred scripture. This was not a game. It was destiny.

He passed the penny slots — too low-stakes. Breezed past the high-roller room — too obvious. His gut led him to a dusty corner where a forgotten machine called “Buffalo Inferno Gold Maxx” hummed quietly. It glowed. A sign? Maybe. He shoved in a crisp $100 bill. Max bet. Spin.

Nothing.

Spin.

Nothing.

Then — a flicker. Free games.

His heart pounded. The reels danced — wilds stacked, multipliers roared, and the screen exploded with color. Jackpot.

Then — darkness.

The lights flickered. Machine froze. But no sound. No hand-pay music. No floor attendant. The screen displayed:
"ERROR CODE 44: MANUAL VERIFICATION REQUIRED."

He flagged someone down. The attendant arrived, eyes wide. "Sir… this machine hasn’t been active in two years. It was disabled. There’s no jackpot linked to it in the system."

“What? I just hit it!” Brettski barked.

The pit boss was called. A security team followed.

They pulled up the surveillance feed… and gasped.

“You didn’t touch the machine,” the pit boss whispered. “It spun on its own.”

Brettski’s heart sank. The camera showed him standing still, arm frozen mid-reach — and the machine spinning by itself.

A soft ping came from the machine.

The screen now read:
“Welcome back, Brettski. Ready for Round Two?”

To be continued.

Who is Brettski? Brettski is a Professional Gambler, similar to the ancient legends Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, Mr. Hand Pay, or Lady Luck HQ! However, unlike these legends, Brettski has thousands of years of stored ancient knowledge harvested by the elders, at skills such as Slot Machines, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, and Baccarat.  Brettski's goal as a Professional Gambler is simple: own all of Las Vegas, using funds made by Gambling.  Subscribe to support his journey in world domination.

pl.title: Nie przestanę, dopóki nie dostanę zapłaty z ręki!
pl.description:
WRACAMY do kasyna z kolejnym vlogiem i bierzemy się za wszystkie gry. Naszym JEDYNYM celem w tym vlogu jest wygranie nagrody z ręki i uznamy go za sukces. Bardzo dziękuję wszystkim za polubienia, subskrypcje i dzielenie się swoimi przemyśleniami w komentarzach. Nawet jeśli mnie krytykujecie – nadal Was kocham. Jesteście wszyscy piękni i naprawdę doceniam każdego z Was za udział w tej szalonej podróży. Życzcie mi powodzenia i do zobaczenia w następnym! Chodźmy na wojnę.

Brettski wparował przez lśniące drzwi Hollywood Casino Bangor niczym opętany. Jego wzrok utkwiony był w dżungli automatów do gry – wirujące światła, brzęczące monety, puste nadzieje. Nie przyszedł tu grać. Był tu, żeby wygrać. Wypłata z ręki – nieuchwytna wygrana, gdzie maszyna się zawiesza, wyją syreny, a pracownik kasyna pojawia się z plikiem pieniędzy, jakby to była święta księga. To nie była gra. To było przeznaczenie.

Minął jednocentówki – zbyt niskie stawki. Przemknął obok sali dla high rollerów – zbyt oczywiste. Przeczucie podpowiedziało mu, żeby dotarł do zakurzonego kąta, gdzie cicho brzęczał zapomniany automat o nazwie „Buffalo Inferno Gold Maxx”. Świecił. Znak? Może. Wsunął do środka świeżutki banknot stu dolarowy. Maksymalny zakład. Zakręć.

Nic.

Zakręć.

Nic.

Potem – migotanie. Darmowe gry.

Serce mu waliło. Bębny tańczyły – dzikie symbole ułożyły się w stos, mnożniki ryczały, a ekran eksplodował kolorami. Jackpot.

Potem – ciemność.

Światła zamigotały. Automat zamarł. Ale nic nie było słychać. Żadnej muzyki do gry z ręki. Żadnego obsługi kasyna. Na ekranie wyświetlił się komunikat:
„KOD BŁĘDU 44: WYMAGANA WERyfikacja RĘCZNA”.

Zatrzymał kogoś. Obsługa podeszła z szeroko otwartymi oczami. „Proszę pana… ta maszyna nie była aktywna od dwóch lat. Została wyłączona. W systemie nie ma z nią powiązanej żadnej wygranej”.

„Co? Właśnie trafiłem!” – warknął Brettski.

Wezwano kierownika sali. Za nim podążyła ekipa ochrony.

Włączyli nagranie z monitoringu… i zamarli.

„Nie dotknął pan maszyny” – wyszeptał kierownik sali. „Sama się obróciła”.

Serce Brettskiego zamarło. Kamera pokazała go stojącego nieruchomo, z ręką zamarłą w połowie zasięgu – a maszyna obracała się sama.

Z maszyny dobiegł cichy dźwięk.

Na ekranie pojawił się napis:
„Witaj ponownie, Brettski. Gotowy na drugą rundę?”

Ciąg dalszy nastąpi.

Jednak w przeciwieństwie do tych legend, Brettski posiada tysiące lat starożytnej wiedzy zgromadzonej przez starszych, dotyczącej takich umiejętności jak automaty do gry, ruletka, blackjack, kości, bubble craps, poker i bakarat. ब्रेट्स्की हॉलीवुड कैसीनो बैंगोर के जगमगाते दरवाज़ों से ऐसे घुसा जैसे कोई पागल हो। उसकी नज़रें स्लॉट मशीनों के जंगल पर टिकी थीं—जलती रोशनियाँ, खनकते सिक्के, खोखली उम्मीदें। वह यहाँ खेलने नहीं आया था। वह जीतने आया था। हैंड-पे—वह मायावी जैकपॉट जहाँ मशीन रुक जाती है, सायरन बजता है, और एक फ्लोर अटेंडेंट पैसों का ढेर लेकर ऐसे आता है जैसे कोई पवित्र ग्रंथ हो। यह कोई खेल नहीं था। यह नियति थी।

वह पेनी स्लॉट्स से गुज़रा—बहुत कम दांव। हाई-रोलर रूम से तेज़ी से गुज़रा—बहुत साफ़। उसकी अंतरात्मा उसे एक धूल भरे कोने में ले गई जहाँ "बफ़ेलो इन्फ़र्नो गोल्ड मैक्स" नाम की एक भूली-बिसरी मशीन धीरे से गुनगुना रही थी। वह चमक रही थी। कोई निशानी? शायद। उसने एक ताज़ा $100 का नोट डाला। अधिकतम दांव। स्पिन।

कुछ नहीं।

स्पिन।

कुछ नहीं।

फिर—एक झिलमिलाहट। मुफ़्त गेम।

उसका दिल ज़ोर से धड़क रहा था। रीलें नाच रही थीं—वाइल्ड ढेर हो रहे थे, मल्टीप्लायर गरज रहे थे, और स्क्रीन रंगों से भर गई। जैकपॉट।

फिर—अँधेरा।

लाइटें टिमटिमा रही थीं। मशीन जम गई थी। लेकिन कोई आवाज़ नहीं। कोई हैंड-पे संगीत नहीं। कोई फ़्लोर अटेंडेंट नहीं। स्क्रीन पर दिखा:
"त्रुटि कोड 44: मैन्युअल सत्यापन आवश्यक है।"

उसने किसी को रुकने का इशारा किया। अटेंडेंट आँखें फाड़े हुए आया। "सर... यह मशीन दो साल से चालू नहीं है। इसे बंद कर दिया गया था। सिस्टम में इससे जुड़ा कोई जैकपॉट नहीं है।"

"क्या? मैंने अभी-अभी इसे मारा है!" ब्रेट्स्की चिल्लाया।

पिट बॉस को बुलाया गया। एक सुरक्षा दल भी आया।

उन्होंने निगरानी फ़ीड निकाली... और चौंक गए।

"तुमने मशीन को छुआ तक नहीं," पिट बॉस फुसफुसाया। "यह अपने आप घूम गई।"

ब्रेट्स्की का दिल बैठ गया। कैमरे में वह स्थिर खड़ा दिखाई दे रहा था, उसकी बांह बीच में ही जमी हुई थी - और मशीन अपने आप घूम रही थी।

मशीन से एक हल्की सी आवाज़ आई।

अब स्क्रीन पर लिखा था:
"वापस स्वागत है, ब्रेट्स्की। दूसरे राउंड के लिए तैयार हो?"

जारी रहेगा।

ब्रेट्स्की कौन है? ब्रेट्स्की एक पेशेवर जुआरी है, जो वेगास मैट, ब्लफ़, डेगेनडाल्ट, मिस्टर हैंड पे या लेडी लक एचक्यू जैसे प्राचीन दिग्गजों की तरह है! हालाँकि, इन दिग्गजों के विपरीत, ब्रेट्स्की के पास हज़ारों सालों का प्राचीन ज्ञान है जो बुजुर्गों ने इकट्ठा किया था, जिसमें स्लॉट मशीन, रूलेट, ब्लैकजैक, क्रेप्स, बबल क्रेप्स, पोकर और बैकारेट जैसे हुनर शामिल हैं। एक पेशेवर जुआरी के रूप में ब्रेट्स्की का लक्ष्य सरल है: जुए से कमाए गए पैसों से पूरे लास वेगास का मालिक बनना। विश्व प्रभुत्व की उनकी यात्रा में सहयोग के लिए सदस्यता लें।

ko.title: 핸드페이를 받을 때까지 멈추지 않을 거야!
ko.description:
카지노에서 또 다른 브이로그를 들고 돌아왔습니다. 모든 게임에 열광하고 있습니다. 이 브이로그의 유일한 목표는 핸드페이(Hand-Pay)를 달성하는 것이고, 이 브이로그는 성공이라고 생각합니다. 좋아요와 구독, 그리고 댓글로 생각을 남겨주셔서 정말 감사합니다. 저를 혹평하시더라도, 저는 여전히 여러분을 사랑합니다. 여러분 모두 아름다우시고, 이 미친 여정에 함께해 주신 모든 분들께 진심으로 감사드립니다. 행운을 빌어주시고, 다음 브이로그에서 만나요! 자, 전쟁터로 떠나볼까요?

브렛스키는 마치 악령에 사로잡힌 사람처럼 할리우드 카지노 뱅거의 반짝이는 문을 박차고 들어갔습니다. 그의 시선은 슬롯머신 숲에 고정되어 있었습니다. 돌아가는 불빛, 쨍그랑거리는 동전 소리, 공허한 희망. 그는 게임을 하러 온 게 아니었습니다. 그는 이기기 위해 온 것이었습니다. 핸드페이, 즉 기계가 멈추고 사이렌이 울리고, 직원이 마치 경전처럼 돈을 잔뜩 들고 나타나는, 손에 잡힐 듯 쉽게 얻을 수 없는 잭팟 말입니다. 이건 게임이 아니었습니다. 운명이었다.

그는 페니 슬롯머신을 지나쳤다. 판돈이 너무 낮았다. 하이롤러 룸을 스쳐 지나갔다. 너무 눈에 띄었다. 직감적으로 먼지 쌓인 구석에 다다랐다. 그곳에는 "버팔로 인페르노 골드 맥스"라는 잊혀진 기계가 조용히 윙윙거리고 있었다. 기계는 빛나고 있었다. 표지판? 어쩌면. 그는 빳빳한 100달러 지폐를 집어넣었다. 최대 베팅. 스핀.

아무것도 없었다.

스핀.

아무것도 없었다.

그때 — 깜빡임이 느껴졌다. 무료 게임.

그의 심장이 쿵쾅거렸다. 릴이 춤을 추었다. 와일드 카드가 쌓이고, 멀티플라이어가 울려 퍼지고, 화면은 색으로 가득 찼다. 잭팟.

그때 — 어둠.

불빛이 깜빡였다. 기계는 멈췄다. 하지만 소리는 들리지 않았다. 수동 결제 음악도 없었다. 매장 직원도 없었다. 화면에는 이렇게 떴다.
"오류 코드 44: 수동 확인 필요."

그는 누군가를 불렀다. 직원이 눈을 크게 뜨고 나타났다. "선생님… 이 기계는 2년 동안 작동하지 않았습니다. 작동이 중지된 상태였습니다. 시스템에 잭팟이 걸려 있지 않습니다."

"뭐라고요? 방금 쳤어요!" 브렛스키가 고함쳤다.

피트 보스가 호출되었다. 보안팀이 뒤따랐다.

그들은 감시 영상을 켜고… 숨을 헉 들이켰다.

"기계를 만지지 않았군요." 피트 보스가 속삭였다. "스스로 돌았어요."

브렛스키의 심장이 철렁 내려앉았다. 카메라는 그가 팔을 뻗은 채 움직이지 않고 서 있는 모습을 비추었다. 기계는 스스로 돌고 있었다.

기계에서 부드러운 핑 소리가 났다.

화면에 이제 이렇게 떴다.
"돌아오신 것을 환영합니다, 브렛스키. 2라운드 준비되셨나요?"

계속됩니다.

#슬롯 #블랙잭 #도박 #카지노 #바카라 #룰렛

브렛스키는 누구인가? 브렛스키는 베가스 맷, 블러프, 데겐달트, 미스터 핸드 페이, 레이디 럭 HQ 등 고대 전설들과 같은 프로 도박꾼입니다! 하지만 이러한 전설들과는 달리, 브렛스키는 슬롯머신, 룰렛, 블랙잭, 크랩스, 버블 크랩스, 포커, 바카라 등 수천 년 동안 장로들이 축적해 온 고대 지식을 보유하고 있습니다. 프로 도박꾼으로서 브렛스키의 목표는 간단합니다. 도박으로 번 돈을 이용해 라스베이거스를 완전히 장악하는 것입니다. 그의 세계 정복 여정을 응원하려면 구독하세요.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
